item.title: Lobão
item.description: João Luiz Woerdenbag Filho, popularly known as Lobão, is a Brazilian singer-songwriter, composer, multi-instrumentalist, writer, publisher, television host and media personality. He is perhaps best known for his hit songs 'Me Chama' and 'Vida Louca Vida' as well as seminal works Vida Bandida and A Vida É Doce.
